item.description: Patch Notes | 1.19 Presaída 5 1.19 Presaída 5 Acabamos de lanzar a presaída 5 para arranxar algúns bugs. Bugs arranxados MC-249121 - Sculk is missing subtitles for some sounds. MC-249323 - Modifying a world preset to not include overworld settings will not give a datapack error, but selecting the world type will instantly crash your game. MC-250034 - Standing on top of mud as it converts to clay causes the player to fall through or be pushed out of the block.
